item.para:
Return value of the special numbering FS attribute. This macro
actually returns the same value as
$node->{$grp->{FSFile}->FS->order()}

para.code:
SetupXPath(id    => sub { $hashed_ids{ $_[0] } },
           name  => sub { $_[0]->{functor} }
           value => sub { $_[0]->{t_lemma} });
